@@TJvRegAutoSave.Key
Description:
This property is the key in which the value is stored. The value is stored in HKEY_CURRENT_USER...Path...Key and retrieved from the same place. If the key or path doesn't exist when loading, there is NO exception.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvRegAutoSave.Path
Description:
This property is the path in which the key and the value are stored. For more informations about it, go to the Key property.

